import pandas as pd

def entrance(df, column):
    df = df.dropna(subset=[column])
    df = df[df['Age'] >= 20]
    df = df[df['Gender'].isin(['Male', 'Female'])]
    df = df.sort_values(by='Name', ascending=False)
    salary_sum = df['Salary'].sum()
    return salary_sum
